# Group Membership Linking Standard

- All user-to-school and user-to-region linking must happen through group membership flows only.
- Do not create or update membership links from generic user management pages.
- Use bilateral membership paths as the single source of truth:
  - `members/{groupId}/members/{userId}`
  - `Mygroup/{userId}/Mygroup/{groupId}`
- Role updates are allowed in user admin pages, but assignment/unassignment must be done from the group context page (school/region details).
- Any new linking feature must support group-style member operations (single or bulk add) from inside the group page.
